## PART 4: THE ASSASSIN ACTIVATION CHECKLIST

*(Grok’s best contribution, refined by Claude)*

**Before launching any attack, ALL of the following must be true:**

```
☐ Knight has reached f1 (loaded)
☐ h3 is played (pins stopped)
☐ Bb3 is secure on the diagonal (not traded)
☐ Re1 is on the e-file (rook active)
☐ King is castled (king safe)
☐ No hanging pieces (zero tactical liability)
☐ Ng3 square is available (not blocked by own pawns)
```

**If any box is unchecked — fix it before attacking.**

The assassin does not rush. The assassin waits until every weapon is loaded.

